      "updated": 1775600084565,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "C++ is the prefered language for making this, since:\n- The main library is native to this language\n- Is easily optimizable \n- We have support and may other libraries to do the rest\nof things that other languages may offer. \n- Low level optimizations that are only possible for system\nprograming languages.\n- Heavy intuition and some experience using it (as me)",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "O4buOwDUzvfpVlnJm0LTx",
      "originalText": "C++ is the prefered language for making this, since:\n- The main library is native to this language\n- Is easily optimizable \n- We have support and may other libraries to do the rest of things that other languages may offer. \n- Low level optimizations that are only possible for system programing languages.\n- Heavy intuition and some experience using it (as me)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
